For List Members in the UK, OFCOM has published the results of it's study
into DRM on BBC HD. For those in the UK, using Myth or other OSS systems,
this DRM has implications for us.
Please take a look at the above stories, and as this is a public
consultation stage, do send OFCOM your feedback. This should be of real
concern to us, as although the feature is only for 'premium' content
currently, there is the possibility for the DRM to creep further in the
future.

